the larger-sized group before comparing the average results.\n{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=Q\n|show_positions=n\n|winpoints=2\n\n|team1=DEN|name_DEN={{flb|DEN}}\n|team2=POL|name_POL={{flb|POL}}\n|team3=RUS|name_RUS={{flb|RUS}}\n|team4=SLO|name_SLO={{flb|SLO}}\n|win_DEN=2|draw_DEN=0|loss_DEN=2|gf_DEN=32|ga_DEN=20\n|win_POL=2|draw_POL=0|loss_POL=2|gf_POL=26|ga_POL=24\n|win_RUS=2|draw_RUS=0|loss_RUS=2|gf_RUS=31|ga_RUS=30\n|win_SLO=2|draw_SLO=0|loss_SLO=2|gf_SLO=17|ga_SLO=25\n\n|col_Q=green1|text_Q=Qualified for the 2016 Men's World Floorball Championships\n|result1=Q|result2=Q\n|col_E=red1|text_E=Missed out on the 2016 Men's World Floorball Championships\n|result3=E|result4=E\n|update=complete|source=\n}}\n\n==Asia\u2013Oceania==\nThe qualification rules are as follows:\n* The three best teams will qualify\n'''Dates:''' 2 \u2013 6 February 2016<ref name=\"Asia Oceania Qualification\">{{cite web\n | url = http://www.floorball.org/pages/EN/Mens-WFCQ-2016-AOFC-Thailand\n | title = Men's World Championships 2016 Qualifications \u2013 Asia Oceania Qualification\n | date = 5 February 2016\n | website = www.floorball.org\n | publisher = [[International Floorball Federation]]\n | access-date = 6 February 2016}}</ref><br>\n'''Venue:''' [[Pattaya Sports Indoor Stadium]], [[Pattaya]], [[Thailand]]\n\n=== Group A ===\n{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=Q\n|show_positions=n\n|winpoints=2\n\n|team1=JPN|name_JPN={{flb|JPN}}\n|team2=SIN|name_SIN={{flb|SIN}}\n|team3=NZL|name_NZL={{flb|NZL}}\n|win_JPN=1|draw_JPN=1|loss_JPN=0|gf_JPN=18|ga_JPN=8\n|win_SIN=1|draw_SIN=1|loss_SIN=0|gf_SIN=15|ga_SIN=10\n|win_NZL=0|draw_NZL=0|loss_NZL=2|gf_NZL=6|ga_NZL=21\n\n|col_QSF=lavender|text_QSF=Qualify for qualification semi-finals\n|result1=QSF|result2=QSF\n|col_Q5=red1|text_Q5=Qualify for 5th-7th place Play-off\n|result3=Q5\n|update=complete|source=\n}}\n{| style=\"width:70%;\" cellspacing=\"1\"\n|-\n!width=35%| !!width=15%|\n!\n|-\n| 2 February 2016\n|- s